| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0010 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 981ff5a5-47b6-50ab-8974-fe20585a0e3e"
